quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  28,85,"'in aladhi 'anzal ealayk -ayha alrswl- alqran, wafard ealayk tblyghh waltmssuk bh, lmrjek 'iilaa almwde aldhy kharajat mnh, wahu \"mk\", qul -ayha alrswl- lhwla' almshrkyn: rabiy 'aelam man ja' balhda, waman hu fi dhhab wadh ean alhq"
  28,86,"wma kunt -ayha alrswl- twmmil nuzul alquran elyk, lkn allah subhanah wteala rhmk fanzlh elyk, fashkr lilah taealaa ealaa nieamh, wala tkwnnn ewnana li'ahl alshirk waldlal"
  28,87,"wla ysrfannak hwla' almushrikun ean tblygh ayat rabik whjjh, baed 'an anzlha 'ilyk, wblligh risalatan rbk, wala takunana min almushrikin fi shy'"
  28,88,"wla taebud mae allah mebwdana akhr; fala mebwd bihaqi 'iilaa allh, kulu shay' halik wfan 'iilaa wjhh, lah alhkm, wa'iilayh turjaeun min baed mawtikum llhsab waljza'. wafi hadhih alayat 'iithbat sifat alwajh lilah taealaa kama ylyq bkmalh wezmt jlalh"
  29,1,"alm: sabaq alkalam ealaa alhrwf almqttaet fi 'awal surat albqrt"
  29,2,"azann alnaas 'iidh qalu: amna, 'ana allah ytrkhm bila abtla' wala akhtbar?"
  29,3,"wlqd ftnna aladhin min qablihim min al'umam wakhtbrnahm, mmn 'arsalna 'iilayhim rslna, flyelmnn allah elmana zahrana llkhlq sidq alsaadiqin fi 'iymanhm, wakadhab alkadhbyn; liamiz kll fariq min alakhr"
  29,4,"bl aznn aladhin yaemalun almeasy min shirk wghyrh 'ana yejzwna, fyfwtwna bi'anfusihim fala naqdir elyhm? bis hkmhm aldhy yahkumun bh"
  29,5,"man kan yarju liqa' allh, wytme fi thwabh, fa'iina 'ajal allah aladhi ajjalh lbeth khalaqah lljza' waleiqab lat qrybana, wahu alsamie llaqwal, alealim balafeal"
  29,6,"wmn jahad fi sabil 'iiela' kalimat allah teala, wajahad nafsih bhmlha ealaa altaet, fa'iinama yujahid lnfsh; li'anah yafeal dhlk abtigha' althawab ealaa jhadh. 'iina allah laghaniun ean 'aemal jmye khlqh, lah almulk walkhlq walamr"